{"tid":1785799,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度反《公民身分修正案》示威擴至大學 警課室射催淚彈","createTime":"2019-12-16T16:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T04:06:47.000Z","uid":140094,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0a1f7670f61c9838b48118818373b6e884631638","tid":1785799,"uid":140094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:02:48.000Z","msg":"印度嘅恐怖份子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iRJ1rgB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiRJ1rgB.jpg&h=8c55f19e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=52iHoquQc-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D52iHoquQc-4&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7kt47LdDf8L2Tg6pYSR3Psk%3D&h=7b75ad10\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=52iHoquQc-4</a><br />\n印度國會上周通過《公民身分修正案》觸發大規模示威，近日擴至多間大學校園，警方周日（15日）攻入首都新德里的國立伊斯蘭大學，在課室內發射催淚彈驅散示威者，至少100人受傷。晚上有大批民眾在新德里警察總部聚集，抗議警方暴力對待示威者及拘押學生。<br />\n國會上周三（11日）通過《公民身分修正案》，允許部分遭受宗教逼害的非法移民獲得印度公民身分，但穆斯林除外，惹來歧視穆斯林及違憲爭議。東北多邦則擔心非法移民湧入，掀大規模示威抗議新法案，政府派出數千軍人平亂。在新德里的國立伊斯蘭大學（JMI）及北方邦的阿里格爾穆斯林大學都有學生示威，抗議新法。<br />\n周日示威者在國立伊斯蘭大學外抗議，與警方爆發衝突，有巴士及私家車被縱火。警方之後攻入國立伊斯蘭大學，並在多間課室內施放催淚彈，印度傳媒報道，部分在清真寺內祈禱的學生也被波及。衝突中近100名學生被捕，大學堅稱學生沒有參與燒車。在阿里格爾穆斯林大學，警方亦稱示威者在校園內爆發衝突。<br />\n在孟買的印度理工學院及塔塔社會科學研究院，周日晚至周一都有示威，孟買大學亦計劃發起更多抗議活動。部分寶萊塢名人如女星Ｋonkona Sen Sharma及導演Mahesh Bhatt等，在Twitter批評警方的行動，Sen Sharma寫道：「我們站在學生一邊，可恥的新德里警察。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20191216/s00005/1576481949350/%e5%8d%b0%e5%ba%a6%e5%8f%8d%e3%80%8a%e5%85%ac%e6%b0%91%e8%ba%ab%e5%88%86%e4%bf%ae%e6%ad%a3%e6%a1%88%e3%80%8b%e7%a4%ba%e5%a8%81%e6%93%b4%e8%87%b3%e5%a4%a7%e5%ad%b8-%e8%ad%a6%e8%aa%b2%e5%ae%a4%e5%b0%84%e5%82%ac%e6%b7%9a%e5%bd%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20191216%2Fs00005%2F1576481949350%2F%25e5%258d%25b0%25e5%25ba%25a6%25e5%258f%258d%25e3%2580%258a%25e5%2585%25ac%25e6%25b0%2591%25e8%25ba%25ab%25e5%2588%2586%25e4%25bf%25ae%25e6%25ad%25a3%25e6%25a1%2588%25e3%2580%258b%25e7%25a4%25ba%25e5%25a8%2581%25e6%2593%25b4%25e8%2587%25b3%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%25ad%25b8-%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e8%25aa%25b2%25e5%25ae%25a4%25e5%25b0%2584%25e5%2582%25ac%25e6%25b7%259a%25e5%25bd%2588&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7kt47LdDf8L2Tg6pYSR3Psk%3D&h=d34fa118\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20191216%2Fs00005%2F1576481949350%2F%25e5%258d%25b0%25e5%25ba%25a6%25e5%258f%258d%25e3%2580%258a%25e5%2585%25ac%25e6%25b0%2591%25e8%25ba%25ab%25e5%2588%2586%25e4%25bf%25ae%25e6%25ad%25a3%25e6%25a1%2588%25e3%2580%258b%25e7%25a4%25ba%25e5%25a8%2581%25e6%2593%25b4%25e8%2587%25b3%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%25ad%25b8-%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e8%25aa%25b2%25e5%25ae%25a4%25e5%25b0%2584%25e5%2582%25ac%25e6%25b7%259a%25e5%25bd%2588&h=9445b6e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20191216/s00005/1576481949350/%e5%8d%b0%e5%ba%a6%e5%8f%8d%e3%80%8a%e5%85%ac%e6%b0%91%e8%ba%ab%e5%88%86%e4%bf%ae%e6%ad%a3%e6%a1%88%e3%80%8b%e7%a4%ba%e5%a8%81%e6%93%b4%e8%87%b3%e5%a4%a7%e5%ad%b8-%e8%ad%a6%e8%aa%b2%e5%ae%a4%e5%b0%84%e5%82%ac%e6%b7%9a%e5%bd%88</a>"},{"pid":"aa2bed525157f20946b4e4945eeaf69c3e30512a","tid":1785799,"uid":13428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:04:45.000Z","msg":"Diu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ccef38fa9c904fdb71e872ef949bc9227a9d73","tid":1785799,"uid":60434,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:04:51.000Z","msg":"打死不離示威者"},{"pid":"d6f213a9c8b0d9a4ff3d03232